flowchart LR
    C[客户端/上游] -->|到达率 λ| A[Admission Controller\n限流·并发闸门·截止时间]
    A -->|有界队列| G[Go handler / worker]
    G --> P[pgxpool\nAcquire 队列]
    P --> B[PgBouncer\nclient→server pool]
    B --> PG[PostgreSQL backend]
    PG --> L[Lock / LWLock / IPC wait]
    PG --> SB[shared_buffers]
    SB <--> PC[OS page cache]
    PC <--> IO[PG18 AIO / storage]
    PG --> W[WAL buffer → WAL flush]
    W --> R[同步/异步副本]

    O[可观测性] -.-> A
    O -.-> P
    O -.-> B
    O -.-> PG
    O -.-> IO
    O -.-> R

    F[超时·拒绝·断线·故障转移] -.-> A
    F -.-> B
    F -.-> PG
